The Supervisor caught an error from its own monitoring workflows.

<b>Workflow:</b> {{ $json.workflowName }}
<b>Failed Node:</b> {{ $json.failedNode }}
<b>Category:</b> {{ $json.category }}
<b>Error:</b> <code>{{ $json.errorMessage.substring(0, 500) }}</code>
